---
layout: base.njk
title: Тимбилдинг — TES Borovets
---
{% set lang = lang or "bg" %}
{% set t = i18n[lang] %}
{% set prefix = "" if lang == "bg" else "/en" %}
{% set serviceId = "team-building" %}
{% set currentService = client.services | selectattr("id", "equalto", serviceId) | first %}

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumb-list">
      <li><a href="{{ prefix }}/">{{ t.breadcrumb_home }}</a></li>
      <li>
        <span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="{{ prefix }}/services/">{{ t.breadcrumb_services }}</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="bc-current">{{ currentService.name }}</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero hero-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f 0%, #1b4332 100%);">
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-accent-300);">{{ t.breadcrumb_services }}</span>
    <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);" aria-hidden="true">👥</div>
    <h1>{{ currentService.name }}</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Content -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: var(--container-md);">
      {% if lang == "bg" %}
        <p class="lead">Организация на корпоративни тимбилдинг програми в планинска среда — мащабни групи, всички сезони, цялостно обслужване.</p>
        <div class="process-steps" style="margin-top: var(--space-7);">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Планиране на програмата</h4>
              <p>Уточняваме цели, брой участници, дати и бюджет. Предлагаме подходящ формат — ски, хайкинг, сафари или смесена програма.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Настаняване и логистика</h4>
              <p>Осигуряваме настаняване в наши апартаменти или партньорски хотели. Организираме трансфери от цялата страна.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Активности и координация</h4>
              <p>Водачи, инструктори, оборудване — всичко на място. Координираме целия престой от начало до край.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        <p class="lead">Corporate team-building programs in mountain settings — large groups, all seasons, full-service organization.</p>
        <div class="process-steps" style="margin-top: var(--space-7);">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Program Planning</h4>
              <p>We clarify goals, group size, dates and budget. We suggest the right format — ski, hiking, safari or a mixed program.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Accommodation & Logistics</h4>
              <p>We arrange stays in our apartments or partner hotels. We organize transfers from across the country.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Activities & Coordination</h4>
              <p>Guides, instructors, equipment — all on-site. We coordinate the entire stay from start to finish.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-6); color: var(--color-neutral-500); font-size: var(--text-sm);">{{ t.service_pricing_note }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact -->
<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>{{ t.contact_methods_title }}</h2>
    {% include "contact-methods.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Related Services -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>{{ t.service_related_label }}</h2>
    <div class="services-grid" style="margin-top: var(--space-6);">
      {% set showDesc = false %}
      {% for service in client.services %}
        {% if service.id != serviceId %}
          {% include "service-card.njk" %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
